<collectingRegion box="[722,895,1807,1833]" country="Mexico" name="Baja California" pageId="198" pageNumber="199">Baja California</collectingRegion>
and Gulf of California (
<bibRefCitation author="Lin and Galland" box="[1171,1425,1807,1833]" firstAuthor="Lin" pageId="198" pageNumber="199" pagination="51 - 62" refId="ref295743" refString="Lin, H. - C. &amp; Galland, G. R. (2010) Molecular analysis of Acantheblemaria macrospilus (Teleostei: Chanopsidae) with description of a new species from the Gulf of California, Mexico. Zootaxa, 2525, 51 - 62. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 2525.1.3" type="journal article" year="2010">Lin and Galland 2010</bibRefCitation>
